OL,3,CNorthern Ireland suffers second night
OL,4,Cof unrest as rioters attack police
OL,6,FRioters attempted to set fire to a
OL,7,Fderelict property near a petrol
OL,8,Fstation in Newtownabbey, with some
OL,9,Fthrowing petrol bombs at police lines.
OL,11,FThey could also be seen taking wheelie
OL,12,Fbins from outside homes and lighting
OL,13,Ffires in them.
OL,15,FIn Derry, police reported items having
OL,16,Fbeen set alight on the Ardmore Road.
OL,18,FPublic transport was suspended and
OL,19,Fsome schools closed early in Northern
OL,20,FIreland on Wednesday amid fears of a
OL,21,Fsecond night of violence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
