OL,3,CNorthern Ireland suffers second night
OL,4,Cof unrest as rioters attack police
OL,6,FMr Ogilvie's family urged people to
OL,7,Fstop sharing "false information on
OL,8,Fsocial media" about the attack, adding
OL,9,Fthat they were left "feeling
OL,10,Fdisgusted" by the recent disorder.
OL,12,FIn a statement issued by police on
OL,13,FWednesday night, they said: "We want
OL,14,Fto make it absolutely clear that to do
OL,15,Fthis in response is not supported by
OL,16,Four family, and peaceful protest is
OL,17,Fonly ever the way forward.
OL,26,@oD@NOUpD@MO]qD@UOUrD@JO]uD@]OU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
