OL,3,CNorthern Ireland suffers second night
OL,4,Cof unrest as rioters attack police
OL,6,FThe reaction to the incident saw mobs
OL,7,Fset homes, a bus and cars on fire in
OL,8,FBelfast on Tuesday, with people
OL,9,Ftargeted based on their race.
OL,11,FCabinet Office minister Baroness
OL,12,FAnderson of Stoke-on-Trent told the
OL,13,FHouse of Lords that 27 people were
OL,14,Fmade homeless on Tuesday night
OL,15,F"because people went door-to-door to
OL,16,Ftry and target foreign nationals to
OL,17,Fburn them out of their homes".
OL,19,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer vowed
OL,20,Fto "crack down on anyone who is
OL,21,Ffuelling this division".
OL,26,@wD@AOUyD@]O]|D@DOU}D@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
