OL,3,CNorthern Ireland suffers second night
OL,4,Cof unrest as rioters attack police
OL,6,FDistrict Judge Stephen Keown refused
OL,7,Fbail after hearing police concerns
OL,8,Fthat there could be "significant
OL,9,Fpublic disorder" if he was released
OL,10,Fdue to "strong public feeling" about
OL,11,Fthe incident.
OL,13,FThe judge warned that anyone who plans
OL,14,Fto take part in further disorder in
OL,15,FNorthern Ireland should "be prepared
OL,16,Fto go to prison".
