OL,3,CNorthern Ireland suffers second night
OL,4,Cof unrest as rioters attack police
OL,6,FThe Police Service of Northern Ireland
OL,7,F(PSNI) said social media users
OL,8,F"highlighting properties" by posting
OL,9,Faddresses online or through apps are
OL,10,F"putting lives at risk" and may be
OL,11,Fcommitting a criminal offence.
OL,13,F"We have received phone calls from a
OL,14,Fnumber of families, house owners,
OL,15,Fneighbours and members of the wider
OL,16,Fcommunity who are extremely distressed
OL,17,Fas a result of this reckless
OL,18,Factivity," a spokesperson for the PSNI
OL,19,Fsaid.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@YO]rD@AOUrD@WO]uD@AOUzD@JO]
