OL,3,CNorthern Ireland suffers second night
OL,4,Cof unrest as rioters attack police
OL,6,FAn 18-year-old man became the fourth
OL,7,Fperson to be arrested following the
OL,8,Funrest, after a petrol bomb was thrown
OL,9,Fat two police officers during disorder
OL,10,Fin Carrickfergus on Tuesday night.
OL,12,FPolice said one officer was taken to
OL,13,Fhospital for treatment while the other
OL,14,Fwas treated at the scene.
OL,16,FThe man was arrested on suspicion of
OL,17,Friot at an address in Carrickfergus,
OL,18,FCo Antrim, on Wednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
